HEADWORD: Water thrush
<hw>Wa"ter thrush`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <sd>(a)</sd>
<def>A North American bird of the genus <gen>Seiurus</gen>, belonging to
the Warbler family, especially the common species (<spn>Seiurus
Noveboracensis</spn>).</def> <sd>(b)</sd> <def>The European water
ousel.</def> <sd>(b)</sd> <def>The pied wagtail.</def>⟦br⟧
